                  , no person being therein, about the hour of one in the afternoon of the <rs id="t17970920-32-cd156" type="crimeDate">14th of August</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17970920-32-off155 t17970920-32-cd156"></join>, and stealing a silk cloak, value 1s. three woollen cloth coats, value 1l. a jean waistcoat, value 1s. a dimity waistcoat, value 1s. a cloth waistcoat, value 1s. a Satin waistcoat, value 1s. a pair of leather breeches, value 1s. and a pair of corderoy breeches, value 1s.
            </rs> the property of the said Simon.</p>
               <p>
            
